        HEY_THERE_KID_I_M_NAIKO_PANEIKO_UP                                    = 7591,  -- Hey there, kid, I'm Naiko-Paneiko, up-and-coming ace journalist. Journeying to the remotest frontlines of battle to cover all the news that's fit to printaru!
        I_LL_TRAVEL_ALL_OVER_VANA_DIEL_IF                                     = 7592,  -- I'll travel all over Vana'diel if I have to! To tell people the truth! The real truth about this war that the wartime papers aren't printing!
        OH_WHAT_S_THIS_YOU_VE_GOT_A                                           = 7593,  -- ...Oh, what's this? You've got a slight air of journalism about you, kid. Whaddaya say? Wanna help a Taru out?
        THERE_S_JUST_TWO_THINGS_A_GOOD_JOURNALIST                             = 7594,  -- There's just two things a good journalist has gotta have, kid! Impeccable verbiage, and a nose for the truth! And, well...and feet, I suppose...to go story-hunting... Three things!
        AND_I_SENSE_ALL_OF_THOSE_THINGS_IN                                    = 7595,  -- And I sense all of those things in you. Especially the feet! You're practically overflowing with journalistic vibes, kid! A natural-born newshound! And I'm not only saying that because I'm tragically shorthanded, either.
        IN_FACT_IT_SO_HAPPENS_THAT_I_JUST                                     = 7596,  -- In fact, it so happens that I just received a hotaru lead! I was eavesdropping on some sol--I mean... I overheard some soldiers talking the other day. Yeah, that's it!
        RUMOR_HAS_IT_THAT_A_PECULIAR_ODDITY_OF                                = 7597,  -- Rumor has it that a peculiar oddity of a monster has appeared in the Rolanberry Fields.
        SUPPOSEDLY_SOME_SOLDIERS_HAVE_BEEN_DISPATCHED_TO_TAKE                 = 7598,  -- Supposedly some soldiers have been dispatched to take care of it. So go track them down and find out exactly whataru is going on, kid!
        HERE_YA_GO_USE_THIS_TO_REPORTARU_BACK                                 = 7599,  -- Here ya go. Use this to reportaru back as soon as you hear something.
        NAIKO_PANEIKO_GIVES_YOU_A                                             = 7600,  -- Naiko-Paneiko gives you a %!
        YOU_EVEN_KNOW_HOW_TO_USE_A_LINKPEARL                                  = 7601,  -- You even know how to use a linkpearl, kid? Tell ya what, I'll wait a while and then give you a call.
        WOOHOO_THIS_IS_WHAT_WE_LIVE_FOR_KID                                   = 7602,  -- Woohoo, this is what we live for, kid! Can't ya feel it!? Now get a move on! There's no time to lose! A cold story is no story at all!
        WHAT_ARE_YOU_DOING_KID_GET_TO_THE                                     = 7603,  -- What are you doing, kid? Get to the Rolanberry Fields rightaru away! There won't be any news left if you don't step on it!
        IF_YOU_RE_NOT_TURNED_ON_TO_THE                                        = 7604,  -- If you're not turned on to the news, the news will turn on you! Now get with the program, kid!
        OH_THERE_YOU_ARE_KID_GREATARU_WORK_THAT                               = 7605,  -- Oh, there you are, kid. Greataru work! That was some top-rate info you delivered. I knew I was right about you!
        WE_GOTTA_PUT_THIS_IN_PRINTARU_AND_GET                                 = 7606,  -- We gotta put this in printaru and get it in the paper-wapers, double-time! It's sure to get rave reviews from our readers!
        HERE_YA_GO_KID_A_LITTLE_TOKEN_OF                                      = 7607,  -- Here ya go, kid. A little token of appreciation from one journalistaru to another. A good newshound's gotta know where they're going before they can track down the stories. Put it to good use.
        NAIKO_PANEIKO_GIVES_YOU                                               = 7608,  -- Naiko-Paneiko gives you %!
        HERE_YA_GO_KID_PUT_IT_TO_GOOD                                         = 7609,  -- Here ya go, kid. Put it to good use.
        OOOH_LOOK_WHO_S_BACK_WE_GOT_PROBLEMS                                  = 7610,  -- Oooh, look who's back! We got problems, kid?
        THIS_JUST_DOESN_T_MAKE_ANY_SENSE_NOTHING                              = 7611,  -- This just doesn't make any sense! Nothing but columns based on solid factaru, and I'm receiving complaint after complaint from readers saying that they're all fabrications and falsehoods!
        I_JUST_DON_TARU_GET_IT_THESE_ARTICLES                                 = 7612,  -- I just don'taru get it. These articles are all based on the finest intelligence gathering. But we can't even sell an issue! And just look at these losses! Get out there and get me some more stories!
        REWRITE_FROM_THE_BEGINNING_GO_BACK_AND_GET                            = 7613,  -- Rewrite! From the beginning! Go back and get your facts straightaru! Move it!
        ALLL_RIGHTARU_LET_S_MAKE_THE_NEWS                                     = 7614,  -- Alll rightaru! Let's make the news!
        I_MIGHT_JUSTARU_SEND_YOU_OFF_ON_ANOTHER                               = 7615,  -- I might justaru send you off on another story-hunt, kid. Be ready-weady! A good journalist always is!
        AS_YOU_CAN_PROBABLY_TELL_FROM_ALL_THE                                 = 7616,  -- As you can probably tell from all the barrels and spigot-wigots, this complex was originally fitted outaru as a brewery. The Federation Forces have taken it over for military purposes.
        YES_MILITARY_PURPOSES_THE_ENORMOUS_WORMOUS_QUANTITY_OF                = 7617,  -- Yes. Military purposes. The enormous-wormous quantity of wine here has nothing to do with its strategic-wegic significance.
        HEY_HEY_HEY_HOW_DID_YOU_GET_IN                                        = 7618,  -- Hey hey hey! How did you get in here!? Were you looking for the brewery?
        WE_DON_TARU_JUST_MAKE_WINE_HERE_YOU                                   = 7619,  -- We don'taru just make wine here, you know. We also ripen-wipen the rolanberries with the help of crawler saliva. Watch out for the spit puddles...
        ALL_CLEA_W_W_WAIT_WHO_IN_GREAT                                        = 7620,  -- All clea-- W-w-wait, who in great piddly-puddles of crawler's spit are you!? You better clear off so I can give the all-clear!
        HOLD_IT_INTRUDER_YOU_COULD_BE_A_QUADAV                                = 7621,  -- Hold it, intruder! You could be a Quadav sabotuer! If you had squinty-winty little eyes...and a shell...and a head like a turtle...
        IT_S_OBVIOUS_TO_ME_THOSE_BEASTMEN_ARE                                 = 7622,  -- It's obvious to me those beastmen are maneuvering for a shot at Jeuno. We can't be too careful about who we have winder-wandering around this base.
        SIGH_EVER_SINCE_THE_FEDERATION_FORCES_TOOK_OVER                       = 7623,  -- <Sigh>... Ever since the Federation Forces took over the storerooms for their operations, my business has become a literal casualty of war.
        AND_THE_FIELDS_ARE_BEING_TROMPY_STOMPED_FLAT                          = 7624,  -- And the fields are being trompy-stomped flat during the battles with the turtlemen. What's an honestaru merchant to do?
        YUMMY_YUMMY_YUMMY_I_GOT_BERRIES_IN_MY                                 = 7625,  -- Yummy-yummy-yummy, I got berries in my tummy!t
        LOOK_AT_THAT_COLOR_SMELL_THAT_BERRY_GOODNESS                          = 7626,  -- Look at that color! Smell that berry goodness!
        ARE_YOU_SURE_YOU_WOULDN_TARU_LIKE_A                                   = 7627,  -- Are you sure you wouldn'taru like a taste?
        THERE_IS_NOTHING_OUT_OF_THE_ORDINARY_HERE_2                           = 7628,  -- There is nothing out of the ordinary here.
        YOU_CAN_HEAR_A_STRANGE_VOICE_ITEMS_ITEMS                              = 7629,  -- You can hear a strange voice... Items, items, la la la la la`t
        OH_MY_GOB_YOU_RE_ONE_OF_THOSE                                         = 7630,  -- Oh my Gob! You're one of those adventurerurers, aren't ya? You got nothin' on me, man./lady.] I was just mindin' my own businesesess, lookin' for junk an' stuff.
        HEY_WATCH_OUT_YOU_DON_T_WANNA_FIGHT                                   = 7631,  -- Hey, watch out. You don't wanna fight me. I'll turn you into meat jerky! Wait, how about you and me be friends instead? Sound good?
        I_TRAVEL_ALL_OVER_THE_WORLD_AND_HEAR                                  = 7632,  -- I travel all over the world and hear lots of differererent stories. I even hear your stories. I can tell you one, if you want.
        NOW_LISTEN_CLOSE                                                      = 7633,  -- Now, listen close...
        OH_WELL_IF_THAT_S_THE_CASE_I                                          = 7634,  -- Oh... Well, if that's the case, I'm outta here.
        THE_GOBLIN_SLIPPED_AWAY_WHEN_YOU_WERE_NOT                             = 7635,  -- The Goblin slipped away when you were not looking...
        YOU_CAN_HEAR_A_STRANGE_RASPY_VOICE                                    = 7636,  -- You can hear a strange, raspy voice...
        I_TRAVEL_HEAR_LOTS_HEAR_STORIES_CAN_TELL                              = 7637,  -- I travel......hear lots... Hear...stories... Can tell...if...
        LISTEN                                                                = 7638,  -- .........listen......
        OH_OUTTA_HERE                                                         = 7639,  -- Oh...... ...outta here.........
        DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_A_STORY_NO                                        = 7640,  -- Do you want to hear a story? No, thank you. Let's hear one.
        WHAT_STORY_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_BE_TOLD                                  = 7641,  -- What story would you like to be told? On second thought, maybe later. Green recommendation letter. A Little Knowledge(pt.1). A Little Knowledge(pt.2). A Little Knowledge(pt.3). A Little Knowledge(pt.4). The Weekly Adventurer(pt.1). The Weekly Adventurer(pt.2). The Weekly Adventurer(pt.3). The Weekly Adventurer(pt.4).
        HEY_HEY_WHO_LET_YOU_IN_HERE_NOBODY                                    = 7645,  -- Hey! Hey! Who let you in here? Nobody's supposed to know about the Federation's secret base--nobody meaning you, not me, you see?
        O_H_AN_ADVENTURER_WHY_DIDN_T_YOU                                      = 7646,  -- O`h! An adventurer! Why didn't you say so? An adventurer! One who adventures! One who seeks adventure! Well, adventurer, is it adventure that you seek?
        IS_IT_SHOW_ME_THE_WAY_I_VE                                            = 7647,  -- Is it? Show me the way! I've enough adventure, thank you.
        AN_ADVENTURER_WITH_ENOUGH_ADVENTURE_WHERE_IS_THE                      = 7648,  -- An adventurer with enough adventure!? Where is the adventure in that!? And you call yourself an adventurer!
        WELL_LOOKY_HERE_COULDN_T_SAY_NO_TO                                    = 7649,  -- Well, looky here! Couldn't say no to adventure, could you? That's why you're here, right? Right?
        I_KNEW_IT_FROM_THE_MOMENT_YOU_SAID                                    = 7650,  -- I knew it! From the moment you said you were an adventurer, I could sense something...adventurous about you, my friend. And what could be more adventurous than joining an organization called the Cobras?
        WAIT_RIGHT_HERE_I_HAVE_SOMETHING_FOR_YOU                              = 7651,  -- Wait right here. I have something for you.
        ALRIGHT_SHOW_THIS_TO_LIEUTENANT_MIAH_RIYUH_IN                         = 7652,  -- Alright, show this to Lieutenant Miah Riyuh in Windurst.
        WHAT_IS_IT_WHY_A_RECOMMENDATION_LETTER_FROM                           = 7653,  -- What is it? Why, a recommendation letter from yours truly! How else would you get into the Cobras?
        COME_ON_TAKE_IT_DON_T_BE_SHY                                          = 7654,  -- Come on, take it. Don't be shy.
        THERE_YOU_GO_AND_NOW_ALL_YOU_HAVE                                     = 7655,  -- There you go. And now all you have left to do is sneak past all the beastmen guarding the path to the Federation capital. Quite adventuresome, I would say.
